{
  "stem": "3605.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And everybody said, Jadzia, come, you go with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Jadzia, come, you go with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because people were told that this is resettlement.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That someplace else is going to be more food and maybe place to work and a possibility to survive.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I knew different.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I knew that this is going to destruction.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I kept working my ways all the way away from those cars.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were, at one point, dividing that-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that platz, that Umschlagplatz, where they had people that are supposed to stay, and, on the other side, the people that were supposed to be sent away.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were air-raid dugouts.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just dugouts.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Holes in the ground.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the people were going there with the permission of the Germans and the Werkschutz-- a lot of Ukrainians helped the Germans in the deportation of the Jews, and they were the guards.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were watching, and they were very mean.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you could go in there and relieve your body needs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I took off my rucksack.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I was prepared to go, so I had three pairs of clothes underneath, and I had my rucksack, and I had a pleated raincoat that I was wearing.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I took it up, and I went into that hole.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, instead of going out one side, I ran out to the other side, where my father was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was a big commotion, and they were trying to find me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I threw off my raincoat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I, right away, positioned myself there and looked around where the girl is that ran away, pretending that I am looking for the girl, too.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that gave me an opportunity to go in, in that small group, to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
